Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Marzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really outdone yourselves,\NMr. and Mrs. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sure to be the winning entry\Nof this year's National Dessert Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for transporting it\Nall the way to Canterlot for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! It's my honor and I-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beg pardon but,\Ncould we maybe move things along?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This here cake's a mite heavy,\Nright Big Macintosh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty then, Big Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To the train depot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it Big Mac, nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is precious cargo you're carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it took months\Nof planning and testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hate for it to-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. and Mrs. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Fluttershy,\Na little pegassistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it there safely, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We never doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, can I see you a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice protective spell\Nas extra insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,AJ, Rarity, one last thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right everypony,\Nwe're in the home stretch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Mr. and Mrs. Cake?\NI got it here without a hitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to do is get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Season 2 | Episode 24\NMMMystery on the Friendship Express{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for helping me get\Nthe cake safely on the dessert car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us all\Nto go with you to Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for the National Dessert Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the festivities\Nwill be just lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fooey on the festivities,\NI can't wait to try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all those tasty treats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the tastiest treat\Nof all is sure to be the Cake's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All that rich creamy goodness\Nof the marzipan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with the tart tanginess\Nof the mascarpone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,blended perfectly with the smooth,\Nsilky sweetness of the meringue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I call the\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the "MMMM".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most delicious delectable\Ndelightful de-lovely cake in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sure to win first prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For I, Gustave Le Grand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,do challenge your crude cake\Nto a duel of delectable delacacies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They will undoubtedly strike down\Nall the competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,winning first prize and crowning me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}le champion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance, Le Grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doughnut Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking up the final all-important\Ningredient for my contest entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Doughnutopia"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And with these super-sprinkles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my doughnuts are gonna dunk all\Nthe other lousy desserts steal first prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and make my doughnut shop famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Joe... your dippy doughnuts\Ncould never outrun me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Mulia Mild.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, my chocolate mousse moose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It will trample all your treats,\Nbe given first prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and make me the greatest chef\Nin Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Mild, you and your\Nmousse moose are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cakes'\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your simple cake could never\Ntake my moose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it sure looks like we're in\Nfor a delicious competition tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should all settle in\Nfor a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta admit I'm pretty beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm gonna hit the hay myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Didn't you hear those chefs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to protect "MMMM".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for super sure that "MMMM"\Nis the best dessert in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that they know it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So... one of them is going to\Nsabotage the Cakes' cake tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to help me stand guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those chefs aren't gonna\Ndo your cake any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are! I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!\NIf you wanna stand guard, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay up all night and protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing and nopony will stop me\Nfrom keeping you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you saboteur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank Celestia, you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But one of those bakers\Nis mixing up something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not leaving you again,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who turned out the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go near that cake, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you okay thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Overreacting my hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was going to have\Nto keep a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look mmmm-marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I think some congratulations\Nare in order for a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hold off on giving yourself\Nan award just yet Pinkie... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been... mutilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we just need\Nto find out who done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, who "did it".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Who did-done-dood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, having read many mystery novels,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that the only way to\Ndiscover the culprit is to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And as chief detective,\Nthat's exactly what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're investigatin'?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And Twilight shall be\Nmy lowly assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,who asks silly questions\Nwith obvious answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we start looking for clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect silly question,\Nmy dear Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the obvious answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! 'Cause I know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, how could you possibly know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, this dastardly deed\Nwas done by the baker
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who knew their dessert\Ncould not measure up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mastery of the\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, destroying the cake,\Nand the Cakes' chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of winning the\NNational Dessert Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, lowly assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well first, if you were tied\Nto the train tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you now here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that isn't\Na totally silly question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And second, the cake hasn't been sliced,\Nit's been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at the teeth marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, my fine fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustave Le Grand\Nis clearly in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means the "MMMM"\Nwas destroyed by another baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A baker whose doughnuts are do-nots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or as he's known in the spy world,\NMane. Con Mane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Crushing the Cakes' chances to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no laser beam security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Joe is not sleek, stealthy Con Mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's big, gruff, and messy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, you would look\Nrather dapper in a tuxedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right, lowly assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm taking\Na closer look at these desserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that one simply cannot\Nlook me in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie... that moose is a mousse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mule behind the moose panicked\Nwhen she saw the mastery of the "MMMM".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mulia Mild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting an end to the Cakes'\Ndreams of taking first prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're proud of yourself, Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, stop! This is ridiculous!\NLook at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was so sure that it was\None of the other bitter bakers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that destroyed the "MMMM".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, their delicious dessert\Nwould reign supreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just look at Joe's Doughnutopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spectacular city\Nof doughnutty delight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,topped temptingly\Nin sprinklicious sprinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, there's\NMulia Mild's Mousse Moose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, this mouth-wateringly marvelous\Nmousse moose tempts the taste buds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with this silky, smooth, yummy-nummy,\Nchocolateyness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why did this criminal devour the\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,while leaving this trio\Nof tasty treats untouched?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have no idea who do-doned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This mystery gets more mysterious\Nevery minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to stop the wild\Naccusations and get to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony go back to your cars\Nwhile we do a little investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay Pinkie, in order to\Nreally solve this mystery,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to have to find clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you were here,\Nat the scene of the crime all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not accusing me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe you saw something\Nthat will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a silhouette in the moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... let's retrace your steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I chased the culprit down\Nthe train towards the caboose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I got there, he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know who did it, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Already?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need more evidence to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard somepony else in the dessert car,\Nand chased them up to the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when I got there, all I saw\Nwas the conductor shoveling coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The conductor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened next, Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I went back to the dessert car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The curtains mysteriously closed,\Nall on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard hoofsteps, a loud thud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I opened the curtains,\NI saw that the portrait by the door
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was all crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What next, Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. I was here guarding\Nthe cake the rest of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I slept by the cake\Nthe rest of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you woke up,\Nhalf the cake was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By Jove, I think I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Call everypony back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a cake culprit to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we all here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're wondering\Nwhy you're all here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have discovered the true culprit\Nof this cake carnage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you see, when committing a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's crucial that one\Nnever leaves behind clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially an obvious clue like... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A blue feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you, Gustave Le Grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, Gustave doesn't\Nhave blue feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, 'cause he's been dying them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how when you chased\Nthe suspect to the caboose,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they suddenly disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they flew away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thief did leave\Na little something behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't you, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even like cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So Rainbow Dash did it! Case solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Case not solved, because\Nwhen we went to the engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the conductor's hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And inside the hat was... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you, that pink hair came\Nfrom your rainbow colored mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have pink in my mane, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're wearing a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You chased a pony to the engine,\Nwhere you thought you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the conductor shoveling coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the conductor at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going down, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But then another clue\Nconfounded my suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were guarding the cake\Nwhen the curtains mysteriously closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no mystery, that's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the thief tried\Nto make their great escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they left a little addition to the portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anypony else noticed\Nthat Rarity is wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,her hair rather differently today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it a crime to change\None's style every now and again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I think it's a crime not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'm guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wear false eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I took a bite of the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh nuts, so did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just made it sound\Nso delectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And boy was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I only meant to take a little,\Nlady-like bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just dove right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At least this mystery\Nis finally solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We figured out who ate the\NMarzipan Mascarpone Meringue Madness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but we still don't know who devoured\Nthe other bakers' goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Twilight.\NYou know what we have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes I do. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Pinkie. Did you find\Nthe devourer of the desserts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I most certainly did.\NIt was, none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the bakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, Gustave has mousse\Nin his moustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mulia has sprinkles\Nin her freckles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, bakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I am so sorry, Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But Pinkie made your\Nmousse moose sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way she spoke\Nof your Doughnutopia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it was too delectable to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well everypony,\Nwe finally have the mystery solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but now we don't have any desserts\Nto enter into the contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can fix that. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Princess Celestia,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}today I learned that it's not good\Nto jump to conclusions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to find out all the facts\Nbefore saying somepony did something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you don't, you could end up blaming\Nsomepony for something they never did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This could hurt their feelings,\Nand it can make you look really foolish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So from now on, I'll always\Nmake sure to get all the facts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that for a lesson,\NPrincess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Care for a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if I do.
